# Transactional email From address

Still Wet uses **one sending domain**: `stillwet.com` (verified in Resend). The legacy subdomain **`auto.stillwet.com` is retired** — do not reference or configure it.

**Default From for all automated email:** `info@stillwet.com`

- Use `SITE_TRANSACTIONAL_EMAIL_FROM` or `brandMerchEmailFrom()` from `@/lib/site-brand`.
- Use `resolveShopTransactionalEmailFrom([...env overrides])` from `@/lib/resend-shop-from` — it always falls back to `SITE_TRANSACTIONAL_EMAIL_FROM` and **ignores** retired domains (`auto.stillwet.com`) and template placeholders.
- Inbox reply/forward: `ADMIN_INBOX_REPLY_FROM` or `SITE_TRANSACTIONAL_EMAIL_FROM` (not `noreply@`).
- Document env examples as `Still Wet Merch <info@stillwet.com>`.

Do not default to `onboarding@resend.dev` or `noreply@auto.stillwet.com` in production paths.
